m/91237832/7059164","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/442237.html?thread=22607485#t22607485","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/442237.html?thread=22607485#t22607485","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/442237.html?thread=22607485#t22607485","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"grrm","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":22607485,"talkid":88310,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/442237.html?thread=22607485#t22607485","above":22606717,"upictitle":"George R.R. Martin: Spain","article":"Some of the Alfies were bigger than others.  They are all made from hood ornaments, after all, and the size of those varied considerably.  The two editor Alfies, as above, were twins, but were by no means the largest.  That distinction went to the one we gave to Pat Rothfuss for Best Novella.<br /><br />And then there was the Alfie that went to Bob Silverberg, which was smaller, but had the added feature of lighting up.  Very cool.<br /><br />Prestige, of course, is all in the eye of the beholder.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"1 year ago","ctime":"September 11 2015, 19:48:13 UTC","parent":22606717,"massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"grrm","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"grrm","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"grrm","ctime_ts":1442000893,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/442237.html?thread=22609021#t22609021","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/442237.html?thread=22609021#t22609021","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/442237.html?thread=22609021#t22609021","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"gman109","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://gman109.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":22609021,"talkid":88316,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/442237.html?thread=22609021#t22609021","above":22607485,"upictitle":"gman109: pic#0","article":"Perhaps for a future Alfie you would consider a Mazda inspired design George (if you Google Mazda hood ornamentation there are some beautiful examples over the years).  Being a fellow Rx7 fan/driver, IMO it would be a notable and interesting award with a bit of trivia behind it.<br /><br />Anyway, great picture in this post, that Alfie really pops between the two Hugo awards.  <br /><br />I wonder if you've ever taken a picture of all your awards standing in formation George?  I wonder if this is even possible as I'm sure many are certificate types hanging on a wall someplace, but I know a lot of your fans and fandom in general would be quite interested in such a picture.  I visualize it being the sort of thing Annie Leibovitz would photograph.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"1 year ago","ctime":"September 12 2015, 16:38:33 UTC","parent":22607485,"massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://gman109.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"gman109","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"gman109","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://gman109.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"gman109","ctime_ts":1442075913,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/91237832/7059164","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/442237.html?thread=22609277#t22609277","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/442237.html?thread=22609277#t22609277","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/442237.html?thread=22609277#t22609277","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"grrm","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":22609277,"talkid":88317,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/442237.html?thread=22609277#t22609277","above":22609021,"upictitle":"George R.R. Martin: Spain","article":"My awards are scattered between my home and my office.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"1 year ago","ctime":"September 12 2015, 19:06:57 UTC","parent":22609021,"massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"grrm","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"grrm","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"grrm","ctime_ts":1442084817,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/442237.html?thread=22611325#t22611325","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/442237.html?thread=22611325#t22611325","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/442237.html?thread=22611325#t22611325","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"gman109","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://gman109.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":22611325,"talkid":88325,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/442237.html?thread=22611325#t22611325","above":22609277,"upictitle":"gman109: pic#0","article":"I recall reading that you have 2 homes in close proximity, and use one primarily for living, the other for working/writing/etc.  I can imagine having awards and other interesting items of note becoming spread throughout the two residences making it difficult for a single \"shoot\".<br /><br />IRRC you did have the media into your homes before for a tour George, I can just no longer find it anywhere online.<br /><br />Perhaps sometime in the future if you're ever able to squeeze it in, an updated \"At home with GRRM\" sort of tv/youtube spot could be organized, I know I and many of my friends would love to see a detailed examination of your collection of Fantasy/SciFi memorabilia, you miniatures, ASOIAF items, Wild Cards stuff, and so on.  Even where you watch your NFL games is interesting to the public - Go Jets!<br /><br />I realize it's asking a lot to allow the public/world/internet into your home and privacy, such is the life of a famous and interesting person I would guess.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"1 year ago","ctime":"September 14 2015, 00:51:12 UTC","parent":22609277,"massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://gman109.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"gman109","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"gman109","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://gman109.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"gman109","ctime_ts":1442191872,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/113789683/6249","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/442237.html